2099:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** * \details
2100:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  The LFSR scale value is used to increase the clock dither if the desired dither
2101:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  is wider than can be achieved with the current Sense Clock Divider and current LFSR
2102:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  period.
2103:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *
2104:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  This returns the LFSR scale value needed to keep the clock dither in
2105:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *  range +/-10%.
2106:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *
2107:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** * \param
