2110:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_1_CLK_SOURCE_DIRECT The spreadspectrum is not used.
2111:Generated_Source\PSoC6/CapSense_1_Sensing.c **** *          CapSense_1_CLK_SOURCE_SSC1   The length of LFSR sequence is 63 cycles.
